{"tid":1632782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有勇武手足，你地班和理非港豬一早就送中了！","createTime":"2019-10-06T22:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:34:07.000Z","uid":202464,"like":21,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"33f938bf960441cb457ae9e13a0740e9368f8450","tid":1632782,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:34:28.000Z","msg":"勇武手足係反送中運動既中流邸柱，<br />\n<br />\n無佢地不畏死，不怕犧牲，我地一個二個已經送左去支那集中營。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無能既泛民？累人既左膠？收皮啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要割都割你地班得把口既垃圾先！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n永遠支持勇武手足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bc8e5bc444336fba628f2bedd2f46e07704efe","tid":1632782,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:41:27.000Z","msg":"寧割左膠！不割前線！"},{"pid":"3c0d71582ec29ca957f643206b9f913b3435dcf1","tid":1632782,"uid":40287,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:42:28.000Z","msg":"勇武好重要，但淨係得勇武又唔得，勇和要並存，左膠就希望有良知嘅每次有活動用大量鎖鍊鎖住自己。"},{"pid":"dae4cfefd9505c3e567ca626ded7161c163c0d6e","tid":1632782,"uid":39872,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:42:40.000Z","msg":"分化post"},{"pid":"de6af30ccb74945f8dda653c73429a4d3a61453c","tid":1632782,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dae4cfefd9505c3e567ca626ded7161c163c0d6e","tid":1632782,"uid":39872,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:42:40.000Z","msg":"分化post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:44:42.000Z","msg":"一日不割阻膠，一日都會連累前線畀狗咬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請珍惜前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5229dc357f6c260459499980f9f8dd87fc16d168","tid":1632782,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T22:47:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">和理/勇武；雙輔雙成；五大訴求：決一不可</span>"},{"pid":"289f202ff19d7870292f7797700381f9a3704be8","tid":1632782,